# New-card compat (wave 3): Elvish Archers — PASSIVE First Strike keyword.
#
# Elvish Archers is a {1}{G} 2/1 with First Strike.
#   K:First Strike
# (CR 702.7 First Strike — deals combat damage in the first-strike step, before
# creatures without first strike.)
#
# Tracking issue: Card Compatibility: Elvish Archers.
#
# Aspects exercised:
#   1. The 2/1 body parses and enters the battlefield.
#   2. First Strike combat ordering: a 2/1 first striker blocked by a 2/2
#      Grizzly Bears deals its 2 damage FIRST, killing the 2/2 blocker before
#      that blocker can deal any damage back. The Archers (toughness 1) takes
#      ZERO damage and survives — which it would NOT if both struck
#      simultaneously (a 2/2 would kill a 2/1). The survival is the proof.
#
# Scenario:
#   - P0: an Elvish Archers in play (no summoning sickness) ready to attack.
#   - P1: a 2/2 Grizzly Bears that blocks.
#   - Script: P0 attacks with the Archers; P1 blocks with its Bears.
#
# HOW TO RUN / VERIFY interactively:
#   mtg tui --start-state test_puzzles/newcard_elvish_archers_first_strike.pzl \
#       --p1 heuristic --p2 heuristic --seed 42 -v 2 --no-color-logs
# The log shows a first-strike combat damage step where the Bears dies before
# dealing damage; Elvish Archers survives.

[metadata]
Name:New Card - Elvish Archers First Strike Survives
Goal:Win
Turns:1
Difficulty:Easy
Description:P0 attacks with a 2/1 first-strike Elvish Archers; P1 blocks with a 2/2 Grizzly Bears. First strike (CR 702.7) lets the Archers deal 2 first, killing the Bears before it can hit back, so the 1-toughness Archers survives unscathed. Backs Card Compatibility: Elvish Archers (K:First Strike).

[state]
turn=1
activeplayer=p0
activephase=MAIN1
p0life=20
p0hand=
p0battlefield=Elvish Archers;Forest
p0library=Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest;Forest

p1life=20
p1battlefield=Grizzly Bears
p1library=Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain;Mountain

[p0_script]
# Move to combat and attack with the first-striker.
PASS_UNTIL phase=declareAttackers
attack Elvish Archers

[p1_script]
# P1 blocks the Archers with its Grizzly Bears.
Grizzly Bears blocks Elvish Archers

[assertions]
# The blocking Grizzly Bears died in the first-strike damage step.
opponent graveyard contains Grizzly Bears
creature died Grizzly Bears
# Elvish Archers survived (took 0 damage thanks to first strike) — still in play.
me battlefield contains Elvish Archers
# The blocker never connected, so the Archers' controller's permanents stand;
# P0 took no damage either (the Bears was blocking, not attacking).
life eq 20
